yang tinggal di sana untuk magang di perusahaan-perusahaan Jepang. Para pemagang disebut "<em>Kenshuusei </em><span style="color: red;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''MS Mincho''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Mincho''; color: red;" lang="JA">ç ”ä¿®ç”Ÿ</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';" lang="IN">&rdquo;)</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; margin-right: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: left; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list .5in;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';" lang="IN">Douzo Yoroshiku</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';" lang="IN">.(</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''MS Mincho''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Mincho''; color: red;" lang="JA">ã©ã†ãž</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''MS Mincho''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Mincho''; color: red;" lang="JA">ã‚ˆã‚ã—ã</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';" lang="IN">)<br /> (<em>Douzo Yoroshiku</em> sama dengan "<em>yoroshiku onegai shimasu</em>&rdquo;)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; margin-right: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: left; line-height: normal;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';" lang="IN">Saya Tahu, mungkin Anda bingung dengan tulisan jepang seperti kana dan kanji diatas. Sengaja saya masukkan di hari pertama pelajaran kita ini, karena Saya ingin membiasakan Anda untuk melihat tulisan-tulisan Jepang. Dan ini menunjukkan juga bahwa Anda memang harus bisa menulis dan membaca tulisan-tulisan Jepang. Tapi tenang, jangan khawatir... Di bab 2 saya akan memberikannya.<br /> Bagaimana?? Sudahkah Anda mengerti tentang pelajaran hari ini?? Jika belum, harap membaca kembali&hellip; Jika sudah,, saatnya latihan&hellip;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="IN">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2015-11-10 21:36:08', 'jikoshoukai2.jpg'),
(3, 4, 7, 'BELAJAR HURUF HIRAGANA', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; margin-right: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: left; line-height: normal;" align="left"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';" lang="IN">Huruf Hiragana <span style="color: red;">(</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''MS Mincho''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Mincho''; color: red;" lang="JA">å¹³ä»®å</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: red;" lang="IN">)</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';" lang="IN">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';" lang="IN">digunakan untuk menulis Bahasa Jepang yang tidak menggunakan huruf Kanji. selain itu, <span style="color: darkgreen;">Hiragana</span>&nbsp;(</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''MS Mincho''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Mincho'';" lang="JA">å¹³ä»®å</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';" lang="IN">) bisa berfungsi sebagai <em>furigana</em>, yaitu tanda cara baca huruf Kanji yang biasanya dituliskan kecil di atas atau di bawah huruf Kanji tersebut. Huruf <span style="color: darkgreen;">Hiragana </span><span style="color: red;">(</span></span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''MS Mincho''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Mincho''; color: red;" lang="JA">å¹³ä»®å</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: red;" lang="IN">)</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-famil