if''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: black;" lang="IN">..!!</span><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';" lang="IN"><br /> </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: darkgreen;" lang="IN">: Shimatta&hellip; </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';" lang="IN"><br ', '2015-11-03 00:00:00', 'angka-1.jpg');
INSERT INTO `topik` (`idtopik`, `idkategori`, `iduser`, `judul_topik`, `isi_topik`, `tgl_post`, `gambar`) VALUES
(7, 3, 7, 'bagaimana sih bahasa jepang itu..??', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">ohayou minasan..banyak yang request..min,jelasin donk..min begini donk..min begitu donk..,oke,di sini admin jelaskan bagaimana-bagaimananya..</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Perbedaan Pola Kalimat pada Bahasa Indonesia &amp; Bahasa Jepang :</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">- Frase</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;&gt; Bahasa Indonesia : D-M (Diterangkan - Menerangkan)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;&gt; Bahasa Jepang : M-D (Menerangkan - Diterangkan)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">bahasa jepang punya pola S-O-P ,,, sedangkan bahasa indonesia S-P-Octh : watashi (S) wa kinji (O) desu (P),,,saya (S) adalah (P) kinji (O)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">klw ada keterangan jadi (S+K+O+P)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">*lho...kok ada ''''wa'''' nya min,,,trus ''''desu'''' itu apa..??-''''wa'''' =&gt; partikel-''''desu'''' =&gt; g'' ada arti khusus,gunanya untuk mempersopan kalimat</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">*iih..partikel apa sih min..??-partikel itu kata bantu/kata penghubung ,, seperti ''''to be'''' dalam bahasa inggris</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">*partikel apa-apa aja sih min..??-wa ditulis ''''ha'''' dlm hiragana-o&nbsp; ditulis ''''wo'''' dlm hiragana</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-ga</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-ka</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-e ditulis ''''he'''' dalam hiragana</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-no</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-ni</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-de</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-to</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-mo</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-ya</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-kara</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-made</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-yori*kok banyak min...make nya gimana..jelasin donk min-sabar...nanti di bahas,sambil -buat kalimat sederhana*min,hiragana ,katakana sama kanji nya ..gimana...cara bacanya gimana..nulisnya gimana..??</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-admin kasi saran nih...orang yg ingin belajar dan ingin sekedar tau kadar giat belajar nya beda..yg niat pasti rela beli buku ttg yg bgtuan,,atw paling g'' yaa..googling laah..pasti ada usaha buat cari apa yg dia mau..kita dr admin udah usahain yg kita bisa..klw bagi tmn2 yg lain yg bisa bantu bagiin link2 yg berhubungan jejepangan silahkan...kita g'' maslah..</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">*aah,dasar adminnya aja pelit..sok pamer..lalalaa..blablablaaa..-diih..klw kita pelit kita g'' bakalan buat page ini,g'' bakalan kasi tau link hiragana di mana..katakana di mana..coba deh kamu usaha nyelem di page..yg dulu2 tmnnya juga udah pada nanya kok..Klw memang bnr2 g'' ada ,silahkan protes lagi,,g'' pa2..*cara belajar efektif gimana sih min..??-banyak menghapal dan mengoleksi vocab/kotoba-baca fungsi partikel-sering latihan menulis bagi yang tau hiragana katakana</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-rajin latihan buat kalimat</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-rajin ngomong..klw malu sm orang lain..ngomong aja di cermin sm diri sendiri..g'' perlu malu...klw malu ngapain belajar bahasa orang..</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-yang mau cepet ngapalin hiragana,,,sering-sering ngapalin vocab sambil nulis...vocab dapet,hiragana dapet.-yang katakana ,admin punya saran..klw punya buku bacaan apa aja majalah,koran atw apalah yg g'' di pake coba hurufnya di rubah ke katakana..untuk pemula paling g'' terbiasa dengan cara menulisnya dulu,mau bener atw salah di jepangnya urusan nnti,yg penting bisa ngerti dulu deh.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">*klw tips kanjinya min..gmn..??-untuk pemula,coba hapalin kanji2 dasar dulu...yang sudah tersedia....</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">*carinya di mana..??</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">- g'' perlu beli buku kanji dulu. Paling gampang adalah kamus, tentunya yang ada tulisan jepangnya. Selain itu, tmn2 juga bisa nambah kosakata. Mungkin secara g'' sengaja bisa nemu kata yang menurutmu menarik.terus coba deh corat-coret nulis kanji..</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;klw yg pemula, g'' perlu mempedulikan urutan menulisnya dulu. Dikira-kira aja dari tebal-tipis coretannya. Kesalahan dalam belajar itu hal yg biasa. Kalau kamu sudah merasa ingin menulis dengan urutan yang benar, silakan cari buku atau tutorial yang menerangkan kanji atau belajar dengan temanmu yang sudah ahli. Walaupun terlihat sepele, stroke (coretan) adalah faktor penting benar tidaknya kanji yang kita tulis.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Kalau kamu sudah bisa membuat kalimat dalam romaji,hiragana dan katakana, cobalah untuk menulisnya dalam kanji. Cara ini cukup efektif karena nantinya kamu bakalan tau gimana cara&nbsp; kanji itu digunakan dalam gabungan sebuah kata.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-g'' perlu waktu khusus untuk belajar bahasa. Bisa di mana saja. Di jalan, di kereta, di bis, di restoran, atau di kampus.atw klw lg g'' ada kerjaan..yang penting niat..</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-Kanji-kanji yang kompleks biasanya terbentuk dari gabungan beberapa kanji dasar. Dan biasanya artinya g'' jauh dari kanji-kanji yang membentuknya. Buatlah list untuk setiap kanji yang sudah kamu hafal. Gunanya untuk mengetes di kemudian hari. Kalau lupa tinggal liat daftar itu aja,g'' susah-susah membolak-balik kamus lagi. Selain itu ada cara lain untuk menguji kemampuan membaca kanji yang lebih menyenangkan.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-Bagi&nbsp; yang suka nonton anime, bisanya di opening soundtracknya ada lyric di bawahnya kan, nah coba aja dari situ. Yang menguntungkan dari lirik lagu adalah kosakatanya yang bisa kita temukan di hampir setiap lirik lagu-lagu yang lain.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-Klw udah ada ketertarikan, kamu akan menemukan sendiri metode selanjutnya yang lebih pas buat kamu. Yang paling penting adalah jangan merasa terbebani. Kuncinya adalah melakukannya dengan cara yang menyenangkan.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">-jangan lupa niat,dan g'' perlu malu..</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Dewa, mina-san, benkyou&hellip; ganbatte ne!!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">oyasuminasaaaaaaii ~</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2015-11-07 22:36:08', '1505586_500579516728270_1800199790_n.jpg'),
(8, 3, 11, 'Menyatakan keinginan dalam bahasa jepang.', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Menyatakan keinginan dalam bahasa jepang ada dua cara menggunakan kata hoshii dan ~tai.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">1. Menyatakan keinginan Kata Benda ''hoshii''<br /> Hoshii di sini termasuk dalam kata sifat &ndash;i.Pola :<br /> (+) KB + ga hoshii desu<br /> <span class="textexposedshow">(-) KB + ga hoshii dewa arimasen</span><br /> <span class="textexposedshow">(?) KB + ga hoshii desuka..??</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Rei :<br /> (+) watashi wa kaban ga hoshii desu (saya ingin tas)<br /> (-) watashi wa atarashii kaban ga hoshii dewa arimasen (saya tidak ingin tas baru)<br /> (?) anata wa donna kaban ga hoshii desuka? (kamu ingin tas yang bagaimana?)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Nb : donna : yang bagaimana</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">2. Menyatakan keinginan kata kerja '' ~tai ''</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Rei :<br /> -&gt; watashi wa nihon e ikitai desu (saya ingin pergi kejepang)<br /> -&gt; watashi wa gohan wo tabetai desu (saya ingin makan nasi)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Perubahan kata kerja kebentuk ''tai''<br /> - ikimasu (masu nya dihilangkan ditambahin tai) -&gt; ikimasu -&gt; iki+tai : ikitai = ingin pergi<br /> - tabemasu -&gt; taberu -&gt; tabetai = ingin makan</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Peryataan ini juga bisa dibuat kalimat negatif, lampau positif/negatif. untuk perubahan bentuk<br /> ~tai diperlakukan sama seperti kata sifat &ndash;i.<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br /> Contoh<br /> perubahannya :</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">~tai (positif)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">~takunai (negatif)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">~takatta (positif lampau)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">~takunakatta (negatif lampau)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Rei :<br /> - anata no kokoro e ikitakunai (ak tidak ingin pergi kehati mu)<br /> - anata ni aitakatta (ak ingin pertemu dengan mu ''lagu jkt48 :D)<br /> - jakarta de hatarakikunakatta (aku tidak ingin bekerja dijakarta)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Untuk penjelasan perubahan lebih lanjut, kapan2 ak post lagi, cz lagi sibuk kerja + males ngetik, kalo ada waktu sempatin buat main kerumah, biyar kita evektif belajar bersama hehe</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2015-05-12 22:37:40', 'bento.jpg'),
(9, 3, 1, 'memanggil nama seseorang dengan -san, kun, chan dll', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Di dalam hubungan sosial saling hormat menghormati adalah hal yang utama. Hal tersebut bisa kita rasakan dari cara memanggil seseorang kepada orang lain. Memanggil seseorang dengan sebutan mas/mba/ibu/pak dsb di belakang nama merupakan salah satu cara bagaimana kita menghormati seseorang. Lalu bagaimana dengan orang Jepang ya?</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Dalam budaya Jepang juga sama, mereka menggunakan kata tertentu di belakang nama pada saat menyebutkan nama orang lain. Bagi kamu yang belajar bahasa jepang tentu sudah umum dengan kata &ldquo;san&rdquo;. Kata tersebut digunakan ketika menyebutkan nama seseorang untuk memberikan kesan hormat. Dalam bahasa Indonesia kata ini bisa saja saja diterjemahkan mas, mba, ibu, pak dsb.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Bagi saya/siapapun yang sudah lama belajar bhs Jepang pasti menganggap kata ini sudah sangat umum sekali. Bahkan kadang-kadang saya menyebutkan nama seseorang + san dengan siapapun tidak peduli dia mengerti bahasa Jepang atau tidak. Pada saat mendengar kata san, banyak yang dari mereka bertanya &ldquo;san itu apa sih&rdquo;? Saya jawab san itu mas/mba/pak/ibu dsb.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Sekarang banyak sekali dari mereka yang memanggil saya dengan kata &ldquo;san&rdquo; tanpa menyebutkan nama saya. Halo SAN apa kabar? SAN lagi sibuk ngak? Dsb</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">ã€‚</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Hmmm... keliatannya ada yang kurang dari penjelasan saya ^_^</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Berikut adalah beberapa akhiran yang umum digunakan di belakang nama orang lain disertai maknanya:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">1. ~SAN</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">ã€€ï¼ˆã•ã‚“ï¼‰</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Kata ini paling umum digunakan karena bisa ditujukan baik untuk laki-laki maupun perempuan.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">2. ~KUN</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">ã€€ï¼ˆè¨“ï¼‰</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Biasanya ditujukan kepada anak kecil/remaja laki-laki yang lebih junior/muda dari yang memanggil. Sering juga digunakan oleh wanita kepada laki-laki dewasa yang mempunyai kedekatan emosi (biasanya pasangan) atau sudah mengenal lama/akrab.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">3. ~CHAN</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">ã€€ï¼ˆã¡ã‚ƒã‚“ï¼‰</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Digunakan kepada anak kecil/remaja wanita yang lebih junior/muda dari yang memanggil.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">4. ~SAMA</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">ã€€ï¼ˆæ§˜ï¼‰</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Adalah panggilan kehormatan. Biasanya nama yang disandingkan dengan ~SAMA adalah orang yang sangat kita hormati. Bisa kepada orang yang tingkatan jabatan/sosialnya jauh diatas kita, atau kepada orang yang sangat berjasa pada kehidupan kita.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">* Jangan lupa untuk menyebutkan nama + san/kun/chan/sama ya...</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2015-05-15 22:39:34', '1471789_262394903907952_1917976207_n.jpg'),
(10, 3, 1, 'Kosakata tentang kerja', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Kyoowagetsuyoobidesu. (Hariiniharisenin)<br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823;">ä»Šæ—¥ã¯æœˆæ›œæ—¥ã§ã™ã€‚</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Itsumoyoruosoku made hatarakimasu. (Biasanyakerjasampaimalam)<br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823;">ã„ã¤ã‚‚å¤œé…ãã¾ã§åƒãã¾ã™ã€‚</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Totemotaihendesu. (Sangatmelelahkan)<br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823;">ã¨ã¦ã‚‚å¤§å¤‰ã§ã™ã€‚</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Demo, shikatagaarimasen. (Tapi, apabolehbuat)<br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823;">ã§ã‚‚ã€ä»•æ–¹ãŒã‚ã‚Šã¾ã›ã‚“ã€‚</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Shigotodesukara... (Memangsudahpekerjaannya)<br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823;">ä»•äº‹ã§ã™ã‹ã‚‰ã€‚</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Kosakata:<br /> - Kyoo: ha<a name="_GoBack"></a>riini<br /> - Getsuyoobi: Senin<br /> - Itsumo: biasanya<br /> - Yoruosoku made: sampaimalam<br /> - Hatarakimasu: bekerja<br /> - Totemo: sangat<br /> - Taihen: berat/melelahkan<br /> - Demo: tapi<br /> - Shikatagaarimasen: apabolehbuat...<br /> - Shigoto: pekerjaan<br /> _ ___ desukara: Karena ____.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Bagikanmateriinikalaukamusuka<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Arif_S</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2015-00-10 22:40:30', '1.jpg'),
(11, 3, 2, 'Bagaimana Merespon Permohonan Maaf', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Ada beberapa ungkapan yang digunakan untuk merespon permintaan maaf dari seseorang, yaitu:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">1. Iie<br /> 2. Ii desu yo<br /> 3. Iie, daijoobu desu<br /> 4. Iie, kamaimasen.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Seluruh ungapan di atas dapat diterjemahkan "tidak masalah/tidak apa-apa".</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">A: Osoku natte sumimasen<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br /> </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823;">ã€€é…ããªã£ã¦ã™ã¿ã¾ã›ã‚“ã€‚</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;"><br /> B: Iie, daijoobu desu.<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br /> </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823;">ã€€ã„ã„ãˆã€å¤§ä¸ˆå¤«ã§ã™ã€‚</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;"><br /> Tokoro de, hon o motte kimashita ka.<br /> </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823;">ã€€</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823; mso-fareast-language: JA;" lang="JA">ã¨ã“ã‚ã§ã€æœ¬ã‚’æŒã£ã¦æ¥ã¾ã—ãŸã‹ã€‚</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823; mso-fareast-language: JA;"><br /> A: Aa, wasurechatta! Hontoo ni sumimasen.<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br /> </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823; mso-fareast-language: JA;" lang="JA">ã€€ã‚ã‚ã€å¿˜ã‚Œã¡ã‚ƒã£ãŸ</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823; mso-fareast-language: JA;">!</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823; mso-fareast-language: JA;" lang="JA">ã€€æœ¬å½“ã«ã™ã¿ã¾ã›ã‚“ã€‚</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823; mso-fareast-language: JA;"><br /> B: Iie, kamaimasen.<br /> </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #141823; mso-fareast-language: JA;" lang="JA">ã€€ã„ã„ãˆã€ã‹ã¾ã„ã¾ã›ã‚“ã€‚</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 4.5pt; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 4.5pt; margin-left: 0in; line-height: 13.5pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #141823;">Kosakata:<br /> - Osoku natte : terlambat<br /> - ___ te sumimasen : maaf ____<br /> - Tokoro de : ngomong-ngomong<br /> - Hon : buku ほん<br /> - Motte kimashita ka: apakah membawa?<br /> - Wasurechatta : lupa<br /> - Hontoo ni: benar-benar</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2015-11-18 22:42:09', 'Thousand sunny.jpg'),
(12, 3, 2, 'jawaban Pertanyaan tentang Peribahasa', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 21.0pt; mso-outline-level: 2;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><span style="font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; color: #333333;">j<a name="_GoBack"></a>awaban Pertanyaan tentang Peribahasa</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 12.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #898f9c;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 15.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;">Berikut jawaban untuk Austen Putra.<br /> <br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">ç®¸ã¨ä¸»ã¨ã¯å¤ªã„ãŒã‚ˆã„</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;"><br /> Hashi to shu to wa futoi ga yoi.<br /> Baik sumpit dan majikan, lebih baik yang besar.<br /> Maksudnya, seperti halnya sumpit yang baik itu yang kuat, kalau memilih majikan (tempat berlindung), lebih baik memilih orang yang kuat dan dapat diandalkan.<br /> <br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">èŠ±ã‚‚å®Ÿã‚‚ã‚ã‚‹</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;"><br /> Hana mo mi mo aru.<br /> Ada bunga dan ada pula buahnya.<br /> Sudah berbunga, berbuah pula. Maksudnya, tidak hanya tampak bagus, tetapi juga bernas. Bagus luar dalam. Berlogika dan juga berhati.<br /> <br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">èŠ±ã¯æŠ˜ã‚ŠãŸã—æ¢¢ã¯é«˜ã—</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;"><br /> Hana wa oritashi kozue wa takashi<br /> Ingin memetik bunga namun ujung rantingnya tinggi.<br /> Maksudnya memiliki keinginan yang mustahil tercapai.<br /> <br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">é¢¨å½“ãŸã‚ŠãŒå¼·ã„</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;"><br /> Kaze atari ga tsuyoi<br /> Angin bertiup kencang.<br /> Maksudnya, banyak dikecam, dikritik habis-habisan oleh publik.<br /> <br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">é¢¨ã®ä¾¿ã‚Š</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;"><br /> Kaze no tayori<br /> Surat/kabar angin<br /> Artinya sama dengan berita burung dalam bahasa Indonesia. Gosip atau berita yang entah dari mana datangnya.<br /> <br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">ãŠèŒ¶ã‚’æ¿ã™</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;"><br /> Ocha o nigosu<br /> Mengeruhkan teh<br /> Maksudnya, menjawab pertanyaan tentang masalah penting dengan samar-samar, menghindari masalah sulit, pokoknya asal pada saat itu dirinya tidak dipersalahkan.<br /> <br /> </span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">ã¸ãã§èŒ¶ã‚’æ²¸ã‹ã™</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Helvetica'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333;"><br /> Heso de cha o wakasu.<br /> Mendidihkan teh dengan udel<br /> Maksudnya, sangat lucu, kocak abis... Jadi pengen ketawa</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2015-09-08 22:43:38', 'Sakura di Showa Memorial Park,tokyo.jpg');
