an class="apple-style-span"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">éž„</span></span><span class="apple-style-span"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''Tahoma'',''sans-serif''; color: #333333;">) : tas</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''Tahoma'',''sans-serif''; color: #333333;"><br /> <span class="apple-style-span">- Atarashii (</span></span><span class="apple-style-span"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">æ–°ã—ã„</span></span><span class="apple-style-span"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''Tahoma'',''sans-serif''; color: #333333;">) : baru</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''Tahoma'',''sans-serif''; color: #333333;"><br /> <span class="textexposedshow">- Atarashiikaban (</span></span><span class="textexposedshow"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">æ–°ã—ã„éž„</span></span><span class="textexposedshow"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''Tahoma'',''sans-serif''; color: #333333;">) : tasbaru</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''Tahoma'',''sans-serif''; color: #333333;"><br /> <br /> <span class="textexposedshow">Note: Hoshiitidakdigunakanuntukmenyatakankeinginanuntukmelakukansesuatu.</span><br /> <br /> <span class="textexposedshow">Ima, naniga ichiban hoshiidesuka</span><br /> </span><span class="textexposedshow"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic''; color: #333333;">ä»Šã€ä½•ãŒä¸€ç•ªæ¬²ã—ã„ã§ã™ã‹ã€‚</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''Ta